features: ANDROID 13: Experience the future of Android with the Fusion5 F202_8G, seamlessly running on the latest Android 13. This cutting-edge operating system brings a host of features and enhancements to elevate your tablet experience. Android 13 introduces a refined and user-friendly interface, ensuring intuitive navigation and effortless access to a vast ecosystem of applications. With enhanced security features and optimized performance, this operating system maximizes the capabilities of the MediaTek MT8183 Octa-core CPU, allowing for swift multitasking and responsive computing.

PERFORMANCE: Powered by the MT8183 Octa-core CPU running @2.0GHz, backed by 8GB of RAM and boasting 128GB of internal storage, the Fusion5 F202_8G is a performance juggernaut. This tablet effortlessly handles multitasking, delivering swift and efficient processing. The generous RAM ensures seamless transitions between applications, while the expansive storage not only accommodates your digital life but also contributes to the device's overall responsiveness. Whether you're working on productivity tasks or immersing yourself in multimedia, the F202_8G's performance is a testament to its cutting-edge specifications, providing a smooth and responsive user experience.

DURABILITY: The durability of the F202_8G is reinforced by its robust design, featuring a G+G 2.5D Capacitive Touchscreen and a sleek Metal rear Casing. The G+G 2.5D Capacitive Touchscreen not only offers a smooth and responsive interface but also adds a layer of resilience to withstand daily wear and tear. The Metal rear Casing not only exudes a premium aesthetic but also provides a sturdy shield, enhancing the tablet's overall durability. This combination ensures that the F202_8G can withstand the demands of daily use, making it a reliable companion for your on-the-go lifestyle.

CLARITY: Immerse yourself in the visual beauty of the F202_8G's stunning 10.1" Full HD 1920x1200 IPS Display. Every detail comes to life on this vibrant screen, offering a cinematic viewing experience with crystal-clear visuals and vibrant colors. Whether you're engrossed in multimedia, working on detailed tasks, or simply enjoying your favorite content, the F202_8G's expansive and high-resolution display ensures visual clarity. The IPS technology further enhances viewing angles, making every seat the best in the house. Elevate your visual experience with the F202_8G's impressive display, where clarity and beauty redefine your digital interactions.

CONNECTIVITY: Connectivity meets versatility in the F202_8G, offering a range of options to enhance your digital experience. The USB Type-C port allows effortless connection to various peripherals, ensuring fast data transfer and compatibility with modern accessories. The Micro SD slot, supporting up to 512GB, provides ample storage expansion for your files and media. Additionally, the tablet features a Docking Keyboard connection (sold separately), transforming it into a dynamic workstation for productivity on the go. Whether it's expanding storage, connecting external devices, or turning your tablet into a versatile laptop, the F202_8G ensures you stay connected and productive with ease.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on December 27, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I chose this tablet based on its specifications and it lives up to them all. It has an excellent picture and sound which is quite acceptable.
